Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.59,0:00:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,远鉴字幕组制作\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}[Visionary] 0day-sub{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.10,0:00:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,翻译&校对：william2568
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.59,0:00:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎来到比肯镇 这是一个奇妙而活跃的小镇\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Welcome to Suburbicon, a town of great wonder and excitement.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.77,0:00:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,始建于1947年的\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Founded in 1947,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.68,0:00:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比肯镇寄托了人们共同富裕的愿望\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Suburbicon was built with the promise of prosperity for all.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.47,0:00:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仅仅12年后 它从几座小屋\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}And in only 12 short years, it has grown from a few small homes{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.37,0:00:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发展成为一个生机勃勃的社区\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}to a living, breathing community{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.27,0:00:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里的生活像大城市一样方便\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}with all the conveniences of the big city{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.84,0:00:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但却不会受到噪音和交通堵塞的困扰\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}without all the noise or the traffic.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.08,0:00:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在这里有近六万名居民\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}And now, with nearly 60,000 residents,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.17,0:00:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,配有学校\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}they enjoy their own schools,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.22,0:00:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,消防部门\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}a fire department,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.44,0:00:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警察局\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}and a police department.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.99,0:00:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,购物中心\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}There's a shopping mall.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.89,0:00:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一流的医院\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}A first-rate hospital.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.85,0:01:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚至还有自发组织的合唱团\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Why, we even have our own choir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.84,0:01:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小镇的居民来自我们伟大祖国的各个地方\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}The people of Suburbicon hail from all corners of this great nation.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.99,0:01:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里就像大熔炉 人口富有多样性 就像..\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}A melting pot of diversity from cities as far away as...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.27,0:01:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,纽约城那样\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}New york!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.19,0:01:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还像..俄亥俄州\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}And... Ohio!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.17,0:01:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 还像... - 密西西比州\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}- And even...  - Mississippi!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.16,0:01:25.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小镇目前只缺一样东西 那就是您的大驾光临\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}The only thing Suburbicon is missing is you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.12,0:01:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在难道不是 您开始崭新生活的最佳时机么\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Isn't it time for your new start?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.87,0:01:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来比肯镇定居吧\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Come home to Suburbicon.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.71,0:01:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 嘿 特克斯 - 我在骑双轮车呢\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}- Hey there, Tex! - I'm two-wheelin' it!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.04,0:01:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哟 你有骑车的驾照么 - 他现在还没撞坏东西呢\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}He got a license for that? - He ain't broke nothin' yet.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.12,0:01:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再让他骑一小时 他肯定就会撞坏东西了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Well, give him an hour. He'll break something.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.25,0:01:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,彭德尔顿夫人\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Mrs. Pendelton.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.21,0:01:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小心点 亨利 我们才卸下辅助轮不久呢\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Watch yourself, Henry. We just took his wheels off.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.05,0:01:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有没有拜访一下你的新邻居\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Say, have you met your neighbor yet?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.69,0:01:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还没呢 他们昨晚搬进来的 我在给他们做蛋挞\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}No, they just moved in last night, but I'm baking them a custard.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.89,0:01:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不错啊\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Mmm, boy!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.47,0:01:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 伙计们好 - 先生好\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Hey, fellows. - Sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.79,0:02:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里是公用事业的清单 订购新一期的\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Here we go. Got all the utilities and a new subscription{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.91,0:02:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,家政服务 迈尔斯夫人在么\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}to good housekeeping. Is Mrs. Mayers about?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.94,0:02:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就是迈尔斯夫人\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I'm Mrs. Mayers.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.14,0:02:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啊\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Well, all right!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.77,0:02:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎来到比肯小镇 祝您在这生活愉快\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Uh, welcome to Suburbicon. Hope you enjoy your stay.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.09,0:02:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是我家的信么\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Is that our mail?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.03,0:02:24.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噢..抱歉\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Oh... Sorry.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.58,0:02:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您有没有拜访一下你的新邻居\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Have you met your new neighbor?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.27,0:02:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把那个放到安迪的房间 这个放到客厅 谢谢\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}You can put that in Andy's room, and that goes in the living room. Thank you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.61,0:03:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安静\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Calm down!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.31,0:03:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安静 我听不到你们 我听不到...\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Hey, come on, I can't hear you! I can't...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.45,0:03:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一个个说 好么\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}One at a time, one at a time! Right?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.67,0:03:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,查克 你先说\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Chuck! Chuck!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.63,0:03:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们不想让他们住这\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}We don't want 'em here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.94,0:03:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想问问在座的各位 谁觉得不介意他们住这的\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Can I ask who thought this'd be all right?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.90,0:03:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我认为我们的社区能包容他们一家的 - 不是我们 是你\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Well, I think we thought that the community would tolerate them. - Not we. Him!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.71,0:03:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你能忍?\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}You?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.45,0:03:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冷静 我们找小镇负责人谈过了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Quiet down. We've spoken with the city planners,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.99,0:03:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迈尔斯家的周围的房屋会用来阻挡他们家的视野\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}and the adjacent homes will be supplied fencing to block the view of the Mayers.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.52,0:03:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那谁来为这开销掏钱呢\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}And who's gonna pay for that?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.86,0:03:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们住房委员会付钱 杰克逊\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}We'll pay for it, Jackson. The housing committee.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.43,0:03:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们可不会为这掏钱的\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}'Cause we ain't gonna pay for it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.05,0:03:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他妈的 谁说让你付钱了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}You're not gonna pay for it, god damn it!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.75,0:03:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我们拿他们也没什么办法啊 - 我们能做些什么的\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}But there's not much we can do about these folks. - Oh, we can do something about it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.80,0:03:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,詹姆斯 读一下请愿书\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}James, read the petition.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.30,0:03:55.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,支持迈尔斯一家留下的人说我们的恐惧是毫无根据的 我们驳斥这种观点\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}"We defy the supporters of Mr. Mayers to say our fears are groundless.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.61,0:03:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们支持种族融合\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}"We favor racial integration,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.70,0:04:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是只有这帮黑鬼准备好了 我们才会开始这么做\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}"but only at such time the negro shows he's ready for it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.24,0:04:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们不求上进\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}"They don't seek to better themselves.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.62,0:04:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们的社区已经在错误的道路上\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}"This community has come too far{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.13,0:04:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,越走越远了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}to move backwards.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.63,0:04:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们要求行使我们的权力\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}"We demand our civil rights{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.96,0:04:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们要自己决定要跟谁住在一起\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}"to live where we want and with whom we want,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.92,0:04:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上帝会帮助我们 我们一定能克服所有的困难\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}"and, with god's help, we will overcome!"{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.64,0:04:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们还记得巴尔的摩 特伦顿发生的事么\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}You remember what happened in Baltimore? And Trenton?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.50,0:04:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是为什么人们选择搬到这里\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}That's why people moved here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.40,0:04:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沃尔科特家的人说我们的房产价值会缩水\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}The wolcotts said all our property values will drop.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.75,0:04:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算我们想把房子卖了 也卖不出去\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}So even if we wanted to sell, we can't.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.00,0:04:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的天 萝丝\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Oh, for heaven sakes, Rose.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.70,0:04:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是房产价值缩水 也是这帮沃尔科特家的人搞的鬼\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}If anybody, it's those wolcotts that bring down property values.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.89,0:04:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是一座平和的小镇\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}This is a peaceful town.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.72,0:04:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出了这种事 人们就沸腾了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}People get crazy over things like this.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.70,0:04:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尼基 小宝贝 快过来\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Nicky, sweetheart, come here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.48,0:05:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亲爱的 迈尔斯家也有像你这么大的一个小男孩 他在门廊那儿呢\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Honey, that Mayers family's got a little boy your age up there on that porch.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.22,0:05:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么不去那\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Why don't you hop on over there{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.16,0:05:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找他一起去玩排球呢\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}and take him for baseball?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.72,0:05:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 我一定要去找他么\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Mom, do I have to?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.57,0:05:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别看我\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Don't look at me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.12,0:05:18.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尼基 你去找那黑人小男孩 一起玩排球\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Nicky! You take that little colored boy and play him some baseball.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.34,0:05:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你妈妈和我把这些扁豆搞定\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Your mom and I are gonna finish these beans,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.18,0:05:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,待会给你做一些黄油饼干\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}and then we'll make you some butter cookies for after.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.38,0:05:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去吧 去吧\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Go on. Go on.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.41,0:05:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想玩排球\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I don't want to play baseball.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.18,0:05:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Hey!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.59,0:05:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Hey.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.91,0:05:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你会玩排球么\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}You play baseball?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.51,0:05:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Yep.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.61,0:05:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们在那拿撒勒教堂后面玩排球\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}They play out behind the Nazarene church.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.70,0:06:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们不是拿撒勒派的\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}We ain't Nazarene.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.71,0:06:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们是圣公会教徒\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}We're episcopalian.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.35,0:06:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那好吧\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}All right then.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.40,0:06:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢玩排球么 - 喜欢\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}You like baseball? - Yeah.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.15,0:06:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很喜欢么\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}You like it?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.45,0:06:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蟋蟀听到了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}The crickets were listening.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.21,0:06:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夜空倾听者她的倾诉\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}The night was listening to her.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.39,0:06:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,突然有一道声音\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Then there was a sound!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.08,0:06:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一只土拨鼠拨弄着一块空心的圆木\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Only a woodchuck, surely, beating a hollow log.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.12,0:06:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 不 那是拉维妮亚·奈布斯\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}No. No, it was Lavinia Nebbs.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.35,0:06:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那绝对是拉维妮亚·奈布斯的心跳声\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}It was most surely the heart of Lavinia Nebbs.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.83,0:06:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她走下楼梯 越走越快 跑下楼梯\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}And she went down the steps, faster, faster, running now down the steps,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.51,0:06:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冲的越来越快 冲进峡谷里的一个深坑里\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Plunging faster and faster, Down, down into the pit of the ravine.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.69,0:06:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就差一点了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Only a little way.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.03,0:07:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过桥 快跑\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Across the bridge. Run.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.77,0:07:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快跑 别回头 别看他\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Run. Don't turn. Don't look.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.90,0:07:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到他你就动不了了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}If you see him, you'll not be able to move!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.33,0:07:06.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跑就行了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}You just run!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.13,0:07:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一条小路 群山之间 小路已尽 那条街道\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Up the path, between the hills, the top of the path, the street.{\r}
