Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.72,0:17:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是让我抓到那些害死萝丝的混蛋\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I ever get my hands on the cocksuckers that did that to Rosie,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.16,0:17:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要扒了他们皮 从他们的屁眼里掏出他们的内脏\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I'm gonna peel 'em back from their assholes, turn 'em inside out,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.69,0:17:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把他们肠子都拉出来 看他们喷血\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}so their guts are hanging out and they're pissing blood...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.09,0:17:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,够了 米奇\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Mitch!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.52,0:17:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不说了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}All right.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.06,0:17:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们服务的怎么样\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}What was with that service?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.26,0:18:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你阿姨睡楼上\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Your aunt will sleep upstairs.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.15,0:18:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就待楼下\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}And I'll stay down here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.13,0:18:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们能挺过来的 儿子\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}We'll be fine, son.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.55,0:18:42.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们要坚强\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}We'll be strong.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.55,0:18:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是不是懦夫\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Coward, am I?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.68,0:18:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我为了你 竭尽全力和约翰·菲利普斗争\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I fought for you with John Phillips all I can.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.68,0:18:49.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你都没骨气为了你自己..\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}You're not even man enough to fight your own...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.68,0:18:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甜味腌制火腿 提前煮好 方便食用\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Sugar-cured ham. Pre-cooked. Ready to serve.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.68,0:18:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可以前往你最爱的食品店购买此商品\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}And you can pick them up at your favorite food store.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.70,0:19:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尼基\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Nicky!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.02,0:19:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Hey.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.78,0:19:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Hey.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.41,0:19:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你妈妈去世了?\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Your mama died?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.46,0:19:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Yeah.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.14,0:19:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她上天堂了么\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}She go to heaven?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.03,0:19:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,估计是吧\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I guess.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.56,0:19:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我抓了条小蛇 想看看么\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I got a ground snake. You want to see?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.75,0:19:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它会咬人么\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Does it bite?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.16,0:20:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会 他没牙齿呢\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Nah. He ain't got no teeth.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.01,0:20:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,送给你了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}You can have it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.85,0:20:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它吃什么\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}What's it eat?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.33,0:20:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蚂蚱 蟋蟀\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Grasshopper or cricket.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.37,0:20:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我那有一玻璃罐的昆虫\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I got a mason jar full of 'em.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.92,0:20:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它叫什么名字\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}What's its name?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.76,0:20:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它没有名字 它是条蛇\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}He ain't got no name. He's a snake.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.34,0:20:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你留着它吧\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}You keep it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.65,0:20:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我来抓虫给它吃\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I'll get them bugs.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.30,0:21:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Dad?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.07,0:21:05.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尼基\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Nicky.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.18,0:21:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在那呆了多久了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}How long have you been there?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.29,0:21:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玛格丽特\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Maggie.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.42,0:21:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 亲爱的 怎么了 - 他做噩梦了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}What's the matter, angel? - He had a nightmare.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.34,0:21:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你阿姨会送你回去睡觉\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Maggie will put you to bed.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.28,0:21:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 小宝贝\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}It's all right, sweetheart.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.71,0:21:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尼基 不用再害怕了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}There's nothing to be afraid of anymore, Nicky.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.71,0:21:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I know.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.48,0:21:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道这是什么吗\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Do you know who this is?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.47,0:21:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是圣帕特里克\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}This is St. Patrick.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.65,0:21:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是你的主保圣人 你知道么\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}He's your patron saint. Did you know that?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.87,0:21:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}No.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.00,0:21:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是所有爱尔兰人的主保圣人\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}He's the patron saint of all the Irish.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.03,0:21:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我不是爱尔兰人\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}But I'm not Irish.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.86,0:21:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你当然是了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Sure you are.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.64,0:21:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的祖父是一位来自戈尔韦的造船工\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Your grandfather was a shipbuilder from Galway.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.12,0:21:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每天他向圣帕特里克祈祷\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}And every day he'd pray to St. Patrick for the bride of his dreams.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.68,0:21:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后他来到了美国 遇到了你的祖母\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}And then he came to america, and he met your grandmother.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.78,0:21:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们一起为家人祈祷\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}And together they prayed for a family.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.49,0:22:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,圣帕特里克保佑着你的妈妈 你的米奇叔叔 还有我\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}And St. Patrick blessed them with your mother and your uncle Mitch and me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.25,0:22:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的妈妈向圣帕特里克祈祷 保佑你\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}And then your mom prayed to St. Patrick for you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.44,0:22:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是么  - 是的\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}She did? Mmm-hmm.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.93,0:22:12.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我们现在是不是应该为你妈妈祈祷\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Should we pray for your mom now?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.81,0:22:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Okay.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.76,0:22:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愿圣帕特里克的光照亮你的心底\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}May the light of St. Patrick find a place in your heart{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.10,0:22:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,提醒我们所爱之人终有一日要离去\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}and remind us that loved ones must someday depart.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.77,0:22:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愿他们轻柔的走过金黄的麦地\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}May their journey be gentle through gold fields of rye.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.24,0:22:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抚慰悲痛 爱意不止\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}And our sorrow be silenced, and our love never die.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.77,0:22:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 阿门 - 阿门\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Amen. - Amen.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.89,0:22:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玛格丽特 真是太糟了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Margaret, it's awful.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.47,0:22:56.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们失去了一位至亲\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}It's such a loss.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.00,0:23:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萝丝接受了神启 耶稣与她同在\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Rose was an inspiration. She's with jesus now.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.21,0:23:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢各位女士\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Thank you, ladies.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.14,0:23:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为萝丝祈祷\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Pray for Rose.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.65,0:23:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里从来都没发生过这样的事\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Nothing like this ever happened here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.93,0:23:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是个安全的地方 - 那是以前了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}This is a safe place. It was.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.11,0:23:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 她很年轻 - 他们还生了一个儿子吧\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Well, she's very young. - And he has a kid with her?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.11,0:23:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加德纳 欢迎回来\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Gardner. Welcome back.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.56,0:23:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听到你的至亲离去 十分惋惜\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Sorry to hear about your loss.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.77,0:23:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 罗杰\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Thanks, Roger.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.03,0:23:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加德纳 这位是比尔·撒克里 新的客户经理\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Gardner, this is Bill thackery, a new account executive.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.70,0:23:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比尔 这位是加德纳·洛奇 财务副总裁\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Bill, this is Gardner Lodge, financial vp.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.37,0:23:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很高兴见到你\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Glad to meet you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.12,0:23:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我也很高兴 很抱歉不能在更愉快的场合认识你 - 真是不幸啊\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Likewise. Sorry we couldn't have met under more... - It's just a tragedy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.48,0:24:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很难过 洛奇先生\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I'm so sorry, Mr. Lodge.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.17,0:24:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 琳达 - 我很难过\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Thanks, linda. - I'm so sorry.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.29,0:24:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们今天有什么事么 - 目前还没有\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}What do we have today? - Nothing right away.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.74,0:24:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕帕斯先生随时准备好见您了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Mr. Pappas would like to see you whenever...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.16,0:24:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Thanks.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.34,0:24:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪位\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Yes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.46,0:24:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,约翰·希尔斯在六号线等待您接听\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}John sears on six.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.67,0:24:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好 约翰\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Hi, john.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.98,0:24:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的天 加德纳 我很难过\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Oh, god, Gardner, I'm so sorry.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.37,0:24:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,节哀顺变 我不知道应该说什么了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I'm awfully sorry for your loss. I... I don't know what to say.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.25,0:24:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 没事的 约翰 - 我很难过\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}It's all right, john. - I'm so sorry.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.56,0:24:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她真的是个好人 很不错的\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Really, she was great. She was wonderful!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.83,0:24:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 谢谢 约翰 - 但是...\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Thanks, john. - Yeah, okay. But...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.29,0:25:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,琳达 我不接电话\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Linda, hold my calls.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.14,0:25:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 先生\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Yes, sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.23,0:25:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加德纳 加德纳\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Gardner! Gardner.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.03,0:25:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你突遭不幸 我很难过\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I'm so sorry to hear about your loss. Wow.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.22,0:25:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来来来\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Wow. Come on back. Come on back.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.73,0:25:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弗吉尼娅 我暂时不接电话 加德纳\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Virginia, hold my calls. Gardner.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.25,0:25:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,挺住\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Yeah.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.03,0:25:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Yeah.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.24,0:25:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没事 埃德 - 我知道 我知道\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I'm okay, ed. - I know it. I know it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.37,0:25:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加德纳\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Gardner, look.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.13,0:25:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想跟你说 我们大家跟你在一起\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I just want you to know we're in there with you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.69,0:25:53.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们..\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}You know? We're...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.06,0:25:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 跟你在一起 - 谢谢你 埃德\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}We're with you. - Thanks, ed.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.15,0:25:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Okay!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.95,0:26:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很高兴跟你谈了谈\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I'm glad we had this talk.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.98,0:26:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有优惠券么 - 这个是面包的\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Got any coupons? - This one's for the bread.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.06,0:26:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是阿华田营养品的优惠券 能打8折 那要付多少来着\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}This one's for the ovaltine. It says 20% off ovaltine. How much is that?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.21,0:26:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,49美分 打8折是..\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Uh, 20% of 49 cents is...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.22,0:26:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算打五折吧\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Let's just call it half off.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.31,0:26:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什么 - 这是尼基 他今天来给我搭把手\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}What's your name?  Oh, that's Nicky, and he's helping me out today.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.13,0:26:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么不去上学\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Why aren't you in school?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.71,0:26:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为他逃学来帮我\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}'Cause he's playing hooky to help me out.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.35,0:26:44.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尼基 把这些东西装到篮子里好么\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Nicky, will you put these things in her basket, please?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.72,0:26:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,逃学 周一就逃学\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Hooky. On a monday.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.04,0:26:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是个幸运的孩子\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}You're a lucky boy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.83,0:26:54.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,12,13,14,15 第五个20美元\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}That's 12, 13, 14, 15, five is $20.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.97,0:26:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别忘记盖绿色的章\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Don't forget your green stamps.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.26,0:27:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,琳达 我不想接电话\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Linda, I... no calls.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.51,0:27:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,洛奇先生 抱歉 但我觉得你要接一下这个电话\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Sorry, Mr. Lodge, but I thought you might want this one.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.56,0:27:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是警察局打来的\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}It's the police department.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.46,0:27:12.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我接吧\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I... I'll take it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.40,0:27:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Yes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.10,0:27:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是洛奇先生么 - 是的\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Mr. Lodge? Yes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.61,0:27:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是盖尔·海塔尔警官\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}This is captain gale Hightower.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.88,0:27:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,首先 您失去了妻子 请节哀顺变\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Right off the bat, I ve got to tell you I'm sorry about your wife.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.22,0:27:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Thank you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.59,0:27:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有别的事找你 我这有几个嫌犯 想让你来看看\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}The other thing is, I got a couple of guys here I'd like you to look at.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.79,0:27:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斯坦福德警方按照你的描述 昨晚抓了几个人 然后送过来了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Stamford police picked 'em up last night and sent 'em down because of your description.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.53,0:27:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们落网了? - 别太激动 洛奇先生\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}They've been caught? - Now don't get too anxious there, Mr. Lodge.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.81,0:27:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有你来确认了 才能批准逮捕\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Nobody's been caught unless you say they have.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.15,0:27:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不然他们只是路边两个相互厮斗的混混罢了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}These are just two clowns picked up trying to kill each other.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.17,0:27:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你们要我怎么办 - 来确认他们的身份\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Well... What do you want me to do? Take a look at 'em.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.81,0:27:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你愿意劳烦跑一趟的话\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}You know, if you'd be so kind and all.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.14,0:27:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我也很讨厌提旧事\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Hate to go over old ground,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.70,0:27:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你真的确定 歹徒闯进来的那天晚上 家里没有现金么\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}but you sure there wasn't any cash in the house the night of the break-in?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.46,0:27:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基本没有 怎么了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Hardly any. Why?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.41,0:28:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,逮捕那俩混蛋的时候 身上可有不少票子\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}These two morons had a lot of dough on them when they were picked up.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.36,0:28:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还好不是刚搬进来的那帮黑鬼干的\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Thank god it wasn't the schvartzes that just moved in.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.93,0:28:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Excuse me?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.34,0:28:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们犹太人不就是这么称呼他们的么 黑鬼\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Isn't that what you jews call 'em? Schvartzes?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.21,0:28:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,圣公会教徒\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I'm an episcopalian.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.93,0:28:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是么 我还以为你是犹太人呢\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Really? I thought you were jewish.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.32,0:28:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Why?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.65,0:28:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为你的姓氏啊\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Because of your last name.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.06,0:28:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,洛奇?\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Lodge?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.70,0:28:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听起来像个犹太人的姓氏\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Sounded jewish.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.91,0:28:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 圣公会教徒 - 好吧 不说了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I'm an episcopalian. - Is that right? Anyway,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.96,0:28:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我自己决定派巡逻车把你姨子接过来了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I took the liberty of having a squad car pick up your sister-in-law.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.78,0:28:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他很怕一个人独自在家待着\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}He was afraid to stay home alone.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.87,0:28:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定要他参与进来么\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Must he be subjected to this?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.77,0:28:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道 小伙子 你能行么\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Beats me. How you doing, junior?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.01,0:28:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I'm okay.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.68,0:28:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那应该就没问题了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I think it's okay.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.05,0:28:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得这样不好 因为他一直在做噩梦呢\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Well, I don't think it's okay. I don't think it's okay that he's been having nightmares.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.87,0:28:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又要他见到那些家伙 我可觉得不太好\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I don't think it's okay that he be asked to see these people again.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.64,0:28:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难不成你是个施虐狂么\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Are you sadists down here?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.53,0:28:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,行吧\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}All right.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.66,0:29:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你最好在外待着 孩子 我们一会后就出来\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Better wait out here, kid. We'll only be a minute.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.84,0:29:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走上来\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Step up.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.05,0:29:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,脸朝前\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Face forward.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.80,0:29:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了 靠墙站成一排 先生们\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}That's right. Line up against the wall, gentlemen.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.19,0:29:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向右转 各位先生\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Turn to your right, please, gentlemen.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.72,0:29:32.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,脸再朝前一次\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Now face front again.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.49,0:29:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘴闭紧\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Keep it shut, please!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.20,0:29:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Well?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.46,0:29:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}No.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.25,0:29:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女士\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Ma'am?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.73,0:30:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点说话啊 女士 你这又不是在挑墙纸\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Come on, dear. You're not picking out wallpaper.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.42,0:30:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}No.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.91,0:30:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这些不是我们要找的人\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}They're not there.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.17,0:30:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想看仔细点\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I just wanted to be sure.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.59,0:30:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那行吧 就这样\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Okay, then. That's it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.09,0:30:29.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把灯关掉 路易斯 你在想什么呢\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Turn that goddamn light off, lou! What are you thinking?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.92,0:30:32.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在这干什么 尼基 他怎么进来了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}What are you doing in here? Nicky! What is he doing in here?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.78,0:30:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 路易斯 把这孩子带出去 别让他进来\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I'm sorry. Lou, take him out and keep him out, will you, please?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.01,0:30:40.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Sorry about that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.25,0:30:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们出去吧\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Let's go!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.27,0:30:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Dad?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.55,0:30:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Dad.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.17,0:30:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们确定么\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}You folks sure?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.35,0:30:55.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我确定\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I'm sure.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.98,0:30:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Yes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.23,0:30:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那好吧\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}All right, then.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.08,0:31:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 走吧 - 那就没办法咯\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Let's go. No winners tonight.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.39,0:31:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 各位\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Sorry, boys.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.04,0:31:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,纳吉利安女士送了一些花来 - 她是个好人\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Mrs. Najarian sent some flowers. She's a fine woman.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.98,0:31:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我们应该请纳吉利安一家吃个饭 - 还有司陶特一家\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}We owe the Najarians a dinner. And the Stouts also.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.04,0:31:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能叫他们一起来 他们两家相处不太愉快\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Well, not on the same night. Uh, herb and thayer don't get along.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.21,0:31:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得什么时候我们能恢复正常生活了就告诉我一声\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Oh. Well, just let me know when you think it's proper to start entertaining.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.03,0:31:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我最近又重读了一些你给我的书\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I was just rereading some of that book you gave me?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.68,0:31:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,《生活如比赛》\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Life races?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.60,0:31:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作者是...\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Yeah, doctor...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.91,0:31:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊万·马斯兰斯基博士 - 是的\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Evan maslansky. Right.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.14,0:31:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你应该知道他书里说 生活就像一场场比赛\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}You know how he says that life is a series of races,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.31,0:32:00.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你赢下这场比赛 然后继续下一段生活\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}and you have to triumph over each one before you proceed to the next?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.14,0:32:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作者还说如果你在比赛中遇到困难\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Evan says that when you find a hurdle in one of your liferaces,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.65,0:32:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要么解决困难 要么换一场比赛\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}you can either remove it or choose another life race.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.03,0:32:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加德纳 也许我们这是在接受生活的考验呢\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Well, I just think we're being tested, Gardner.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.76,0:32:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许吧 玛格丽特\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Maybe, Margaret.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.76,0:32:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 萝丝的不幸 这就是我们面对的困难 - 是的 我们选择换一场比赛\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Rose's accident, that was a hurdle. - It was. And we chose another race.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.26,0:32:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 如果你积蓄都花光了 就又是新的困难了 - 是啊\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}And when you lost your life savings, that was another hurdle.  Hmm.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.46,0:32:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们也可以解决这个困难\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}And we'll triumph over this one as well.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.46,0:32:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你很坚强 加德纳 尼基也一样\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Because you're strong, Gardner. And so is Nicky.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.15,0:32:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们能一起挺过去的 对么 尼基\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}And we're gonna get through this together, aren't we, Nicky?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.76,0:32:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你感觉如何 儿子\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}How you feeling, son?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.27,0:33:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Fine.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.48,0:33:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天真不容易\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}It's been a rough day.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.96,0:33:10.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Dad?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.34,0:33:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么能说那人不是他\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}How come you said it wasn't them?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.05,0:33:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说谁\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Wasn't who?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.73,0:33:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是那些歹徒\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}The robbers{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.41,0:33:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,害死了妈妈的歹徒\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}who killed mom.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.13,0:33:27.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尼基 你看到了那些排队的人么\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Nicky, did you see the line-up?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.04,0:33:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我看到... - 那些肯定不是我们要找的歹徒\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I saw... Because that certainly was not the robbers.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.73,0:33:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不是\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}It certainly was not.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.10,0:33:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我觉得.. - 孩子 我想让你明白一些事\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}But I thought... Young man, I want you to understand something.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.37,0:33:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人们每天走进我的办公室\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}People walk into my office every day,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.93,0:33:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,声称他们见过我 但我从来都不记得他们\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}say they've met me, I don't remember them at all.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.89,0:33:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有些时候 我看到一些人 以为我认识他们\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Or sometimes I see people that I think I know, and then,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.35,0:33:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然而他们却说并没有见过我\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}later, they tell me that we've never met.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.61,0:33:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许他们长得像某人 他们的说话方式像某人\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Maybe they look like someone else. Maybe they talk like someone else.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.12,0:33:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能这两人是有联系的\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Maybe they're even related.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.16,0:34:00.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 爸爸 我看见了 - 我的意思是\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}But, dad, I saw. No, no, my point... my point{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.80,0:34:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你到底认不认识一个人 这是说不清楚的\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}is that it's a very tricky business this who you know and who you don't know.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.44,0:34:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我告诉你\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}And I'm telling you{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.55,0:34:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我仔细的看过了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}that I got a good look at those clowns,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.29,0:34:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们不是我们要找的人\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}and I've never seen them before.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.82,0:34:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 米奇叔叔说 - 米奇叔叔不重要\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Uncle Mitch promised that... - Uncle Mitch doesn't matter.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.82,0:34:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,米奇叔叔就是个蠢蛋\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Uncle Mitch is a buffoon.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.92,0:34:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是我们自家的事 你不要跟米奇叔叔说\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Now, this is a family matter, and I don't want you talking to uncle Mitch about it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.11,0:34:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白了么\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Is that understood?{\r}
