Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.89,0:45:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的 什么“洛奇先生打电话来了”\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}"Mrs. Lodge called." Swear to god!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.40,0:45:19.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 真是奇怪啊 - 是啊 真奇怪\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}That's very strange. Strange? Yeah, strange.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.61,0:45:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要去看看你们 见一下尼基\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I should come visit. Come see Nicky.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.94,0:45:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,米奇\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Mitch...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.61,0:45:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我们缓缓吧\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Give us a while. Huh?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.84,0:45:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,挺煎熬的 我知道对你来说也挺煎熬的\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}It's been hard for us. And I know it's been hard for you, too.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.31,0:45:35.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 但是我们这段时间不希望有访客 尼基需要点时间\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I'm sorry. But no visitors, just for a while. Nicky needs time.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.78,0:45:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,时间\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Time?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.48,0:45:38.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么时间\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}For what, time?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.23,0:45:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再见 米奇\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Bye, Mitch.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.47,0:45:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把他们组合在一起 建造一座城堡\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Just snap 'em together and build a castle!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.93,0:45:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或是张凳子\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Or a chair.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.10,0:45:56.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尼基\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Nicky?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.89,0:45:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你父亲想跟你谈谈\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Your father would like to have a word with you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.49,0:46:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,猴子积木很好玩的\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Monkey sticks are fun!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.96,0:46:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下雨天的时候 你要待在家里\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Even on rainy days, when you have to stay in.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.77,0:46:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,进来\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Yes?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.14,0:46:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把门关上 尼古拉斯\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Shut the door, Nicholas.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.59,0:46:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坐下\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Have a seat.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.47,0:46:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尼基\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Nick,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.36,0:46:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直想让你守点\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I've tried to instill in you a certain{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.06,0:46:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,规矩\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}discipline.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.47,0:46:42.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得你的母亲太溺爱你了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Your mother indulged you, I think.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.40,0:46:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这其实没什么问题\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}And that's fine, up to a certain point.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.41,0:46:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她很想保护你 没什么问题\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}The cocoon and so forth. That's fine.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.03,0:46:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但现在我们\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}But now we...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.52,0:46:55.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们现在来好好分析一下 现在是个什么情况\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}We draw the ledger, and we... we see where we are.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.16,0:46:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白我说的话么\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}You understand?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.32,0:46:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白 爸爸\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Yes, sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.22,0:47:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我面前这位小男孩 闷闷不乐\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I see a little boy who is sullen.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.67,0:47:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我面前这位小男孩 沉默寡言\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I see a little boy who is frequently withdrawn,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.70,0:47:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沉浸在自己的世界里\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}in his own little world.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.26,0:47:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有朋友\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Little boy with no friends.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.57,0:47:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不合群\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Doesn't fit in.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.14,0:47:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这些很重要 尼古拉斯 对于这些问题我们不能一笑置之\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}These things are important, Nicholas. We don't laugh off these things.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.07,0:47:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}So{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.68,0:47:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和你阿姨在找一个寄宿学校\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}we've been looking into sleepaway school.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.36,0:47:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那里小伙子们会学会遵守纪律 学会合群\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}A place where young men learn about discipline and fitting in and...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.57,0:47:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚会飞的幼鸟总是对鸟巢恋恋不舍 尼古拉斯 你觉得它这样好么\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}The fledgling always wants the nest, Nicholas, but is it good for him?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.06,0:47:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这对他来说好么 我们咨询了一些专家\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Is it good for him? Well, we've consulted the experts.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.86,0:47:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得不好\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I think not.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.54,0:47:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得不好\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I think not.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.07,0:47:53.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以你的阿姨玛格丽特和我决定\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}So your aunt maggie and I have decided{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.88,0:47:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,送你去 巴特尔克里克军校\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}that Battle Creek, the academy,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.59,0:48:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是最好的选择\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}is the best solution.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.80,0:48:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下学期送你去\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}And starting next semester,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.99,0:48:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们会给军校新生腾出位置\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}they've made room for a new plebe.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.16,0:48:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我找了些关系才得以让你顺利入学\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I had to pull a few strings to get you in, but...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.63,0:48:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你啊\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Congratulations.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.47,0:48:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}巴特尔克里克军校 年轻人准备迎接新生活
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.78,0:48:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个要20美元\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}That's $20.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.60,0:49:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先生 标价牌上写的可不是20美元\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Well, sir, that wasn't the price on the display.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.54,0:49:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,涨价了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}The price went up.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.57,0:49:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,涨到20美元了?\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}To $20?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.14,0:49:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得这个也要收20美元 对吧 玛格丽特\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I believe that's $20 also, isn't it, Margaret?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.96,0:49:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是20美元\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}It's $20.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.70,0:49:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能问你一个问题么\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}May I ask you a question?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.19,0:49:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得你在别的店会有更不错的价格\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I think you'll find the prices much better elsewhere.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.63,0:49:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也这么认为\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I imagine that's true.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.98,0:49:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别担心 我们会把这些放回去的\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Don't worry. We'll put these back!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.24,0:50:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让吉米把这些摆回货架上\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Have jimmy restock.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.45,0:50:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在不久的将来\N♪ in the sweet by and by
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.13,0:50:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们将在这美丽的海岸相遇\N♪ we shall meet on that beautiful shore
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.99,0:50:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在不久的将来\N♪ in the sweet by and by
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.57,0:50:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们将在这美丽的海岸相遇\N♪ we shall meet on that beautiful shore
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.99,0:50:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在不久的将来，\N♪ in the sweet by and by♪
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.83,0:50:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们觉得如果这里住的都是白人\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}...And we understood that it was going to be all white.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.82,0:50:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们就很愿意在这里定居\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}We were very happy to buy a home here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.78,0:50:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得一户黑人家庭会影响到整个社区么\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Do you think a negro family moving here will affect the community as a whole?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.98,0:50:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绝对如此 - 此话怎讲\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Definitely.  In what way?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.85,0:50:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们以前住在华盛顿 我在那就遇到了一个这样的情况\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}We used to live in Washington, DC, and we saw a very good example of that there.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.74,0:50:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个种族融合所带来的麻烦在于\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}The whole trouble with this integration business is{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.83,0:51:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最后 种族间社会交往也会趋于融合\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}that, in the end, it probably will end up with mixing socially.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.97,0:51:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比如会有\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}And you will have...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.07,0:51:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得他们的目标是种族通婚\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Well, I think their aim is mixed marriages{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.37,0:51:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,黑人白人平等\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}and becoming equal with the whites.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.07,0:51:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但他们想要达到这个目标\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}But the only way they're gonna do that{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.07,0:51:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是通过教育提升自己\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}is by education and by bettering themselves,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.15,0:51:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而不是固守他们原来的样子\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}not by pushing in the way they have here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.47,0:51:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等我们拿到了那笔保险费\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Soon as we get the insurance money,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.02,0:51:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一切都会好起来的\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}everything will be fine.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.35,0:51:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们可以去阿鲁巴岛\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}We could go to Aruba.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.58,0:51:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿鲁巴岛?那是什么地方\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Aruba? Where's that?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.76,0:51:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是在加勒比海\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Oh, it's in the Caribbean.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.86,0:51:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是荷兰的保护国\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}It's a Dutch protectorate.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.73,0:51:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和美国没有签订引渡协议\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}There's no reciprocal extradition.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.49,0:51:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我从来没有去过保护国\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I've never been to a protectorate before.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.53,0:51:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们可以从别的岛坐船过去 不留票据痕迹\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}We could take a boat from another island. Leave no ticket trail.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.36,0:51:51.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是可以吃上麻辣芒果食物\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Well, isn't it spicy mango food?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.37,0:51:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想吃什么美食都有 应有尽有\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Oh, you can get any sort of food. Food of any description.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.03,0:52:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还可以打高尔夫 双人高尔夫球\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}And there's golfing. Couples golfing.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.23,0:52:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟萝丝去过好几次 - 那挺不错的\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I went with Rose many times. Oh, that's good.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.01,0:52:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亲爱的 你可以好好放松\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Darling, you could relax{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.53,0:52:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作画\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}and paint.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.68,0:52:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,展现自我\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Express yourself.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.91,0:52:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我从来没有真正展现过自我\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}You never really express yourself.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.19,0:52:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很爱萝丝\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I loved Rose, but{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.18,0:52:25.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你需要别人来帮你放开自我\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}you need someone to help you do that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.58,0:52:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我说的这个别人是谁么\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}And do you know who that someone is?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.05,0:52:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那让我好好想想\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Well, let me think about that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.94,0:52:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想啊\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}You do that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.46,0:52:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玛莎·斯陶特是一位非常友好的人\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Well, Martha Stout is awfully friendly.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.56,0:52:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我来提醒你一下\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Oh, well, let me try to jog your memory.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.23,0:52:49.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加德纳 我们早就该这么做了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}We should have done this a long time ago, Gardner.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.94,0:52:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你只是困住了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}You were trapped.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.02,0:53:04.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,洛奇先生 海塔尔警官来访\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Mr. Lodge, I have a lieutenant Hightower.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.93,0:53:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟他说我不在\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Tell him I'm not in.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.65,0:53:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先生 开了免提的\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}You're on speaker, sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.13,0:53:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 警官 我现在正忙着\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Sorry, lieutenant. You've come at a very busy time.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.38,0:53:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉我这么仓促来访\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Well, I'm sorry to drop in on you like this.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.61,0:53:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最近有了一些新情况 我想了解一下\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I wanted to clear something up that's just come to light.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.05,0:53:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你近来如何\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}What happened to you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.72,0:53:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就带带孩子\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Horsing around with my kid.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.01,0:53:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 孩子现在还好吧 - 是啊\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}He's got a mean right. He does.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.40,0:53:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,调查进展如何了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}So any new progress on the investigation?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.56,0:53:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其实我是想觉得有另外一个案子 你应该能帮上忙\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Well, actually, I was hoping you might be able to help me with another case.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.81,0:53:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你认不认识一个叫瑞佐立的人?\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}You know a character named Rizzoli?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.80,0:53:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瑞佐立?没听说过\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}No. Rizzoli? No.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.38,0:53:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他几天前 在一辆停在收费公路上的运输车里 遇害\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}He got killed in a vehicular on the turnpike a couple days ago.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.84,0:53:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他叫瑞佐立 弗兰克·瑞佐立\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Rizzoli. Frank Rizzoli?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.07,0:53:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从没听说过这个人\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Never heard of him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.06,0:54:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个消息真是让我感到遗憾\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I'm sorry for his loss.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.60,0:54:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是说他离世让你遗憾?\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Of life?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.93,0:54:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 估计他自己也觉得很遗憾\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Yeah, I guess he probably is, too.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.88,0:54:10.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是为一些恶棍放高利贷的 所以我觉得他也算是死有余辜\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}He was a loan shark for the mob, so I wouldn't feel too bad.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.60,0:54:14.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有什么能帮上忙的么\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Then how can I help?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.19,0:54:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们查阅了他的笔记本\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Well, we've been going through his books.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.15,0:54:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么记账本啊 笔记本啊\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}He has all these books. Notes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.69,0:54:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是用暗号写的\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}All in code.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.89,0:54:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比如\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Like,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.71,0:54:30.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比肯小镇 剃发刮胡 8500\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}"Suburbicon shave and a haircut, 8,500 long."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.08,0:54:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剃发刮胡收这么多钱貌似很罕见啊\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Seems like a lot of cash for a shave and a haircut.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.16,0:54:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算是在富有的比肯镇也很少见\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Even for Suburbicon.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:38.03,0:54:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你继续往下读的话 有这么一条很奇怪的记录\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}But if you keep reading down, it has this one very odd...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.87,0:54:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是这么说的 “从加德纳·洛奇处”拿了7000苹果\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}It says, "pick up package of 7,000 apples "at Gardner Lodge."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.89,0:54:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这说的是你吧\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}And that's your name.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.62,0:54:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我翻找了一下黄页 在其中\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}But we started looking through phone books, and lo and behold,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.82,0:55:01.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到特伦顿附近有一家宾馆叫“加德·洛奇”\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}we found a hotel up near Trenton called garden Lodge.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.41,0:55:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以 他要么是想从住在加德·洛奇宾馆里的某个人\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}So either he was expecting 7,000 apples{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.67,0:55:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那里拿到“7000苹果”\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}from someone at garden Lodge,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.78,0:55:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要么就是从你这里拿到\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}or he expected them from you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.61,0:55:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,洛奇先生 我现在不是在审问你\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Now, I'm not asking you, Mr. Lodge,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.15,0:55:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你问恶棍借钱\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}if you were into the mob for money.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.46,0:55:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你借了的话 不管你是没有付\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}But if you were, and if you didn't pay or{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.10,0:55:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是根本付不起\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}couldn't pay,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.08,0:55:28.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}well,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.81,0:55:31.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许就能解释发生在你妻子身上的不幸了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}that might explain what happened to your wife.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.98,0:55:36.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你说你不认识他\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}But you say you don't know him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.99,0:55:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我确实不认识他\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I don't know him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.15,0:55:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Well,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.23,0:55:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们继续调查\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}we'll keep looking.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.68,0:55:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 警官\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Thank you, lieutenant.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.95,0:55:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们保持联系\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I'll be in touch.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.62,0:56:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一些人是完全反对种族融合的\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Some of the people are definitely against integration.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.62,0:56:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们告诉自己的孩子\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}And they have told my children{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.72,0:56:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们未来可能要与黑鬼结婚\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}That they have to marry niggers.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.47,0:56:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的孩子甚至都不知道黑鬼是什么\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}And my child doesn't even know what a nigger is.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:29.50,0:56:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么事\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Yes?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.22,0:56:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奥罗瑞小姐 我是坎宁生命保险公司的巴德·库珀\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Miss o'Rory, I'm Bud Cooper with Canyon Prop and Life.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.77,0:56:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢您 库珀先生\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Oh, well, thank you very much, Mr. Cooper,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.04,0:56:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我觉得我们现在应该不用保险\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}but I'm quite sure we have all the insurance that we need.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.51,0:56:41.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 但其实 我不是保险推销员\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I'm sure you do, but fact is, I'm not a salesman.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:41.24,0:56:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是来商量一下您姐姐的保险赔偿事宜的\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I'm here to discuss your sister's policy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.81,0:56:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个问题你恐怕和一家之主谈一下比较好\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Oh, you'd have to talk to the man of the house about that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.03,0:56:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他了解具体情况 他晚上才回来\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}He has all the information. He'll be back this evening.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.37,0:56:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能不能让我进来坐坐\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Could... Can I just come in for a second?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:52.78,0:56:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些情况我真的一点都不了解啊\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Well, I don't have any of the information.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.99,0:56:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 奥罗瑞小姐 我只是想来跟您聊一会儿\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Oh, no, it doesn't matter, Miss O'Rory. I'd just like to chat with you for a minute.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.55,0:57:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真的不知道 我有什么能帮到你的\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Oh, I haven't the faintest idea how I can help you...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.75,0:57:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我什么都不知道啊\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Since I don't have any of the information.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.13,0:57:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说你是保险公司来的 具体是做什么的\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}What did you say you do for the insurance people?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:13.21,0:57:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得我的职务全称叫做 索赔调查员\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I guess my official title is claims investigator.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:16.69,0:57:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也可以叫我职业挑刺员\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}What you might call a professional skeptic.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:18.94,0:57:21.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以保险合同方面有什么问题么\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Okay. Is there something wrong with the policy?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:21.90,0:57:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不不不 保险合同是没什么问题的\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}No, no, no! Policy seems to be all shipshape.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.33,0:57:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,洛奇先生按时缴纳保险费\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Yes, Mr. Lodge has been very steady with the payments.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:27.79,0:57:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当时接待的保险员是\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Your agent...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.54,0:57:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 埃尔金斯先生 - 是的 斯坦·埃尔金斯\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Mr. Elkins? Right. Stan Elkins.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:35.45,0:57:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他说你们一切正常 你有见过他么\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Yes, he says everything's in order. Have you met him?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.77,0:57:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有 加德纳先生这方面的事我都不清楚\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Oh, no. I don't know anything about Gardner's business affairs.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:40.23,0:57:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我觉得我没什么能帮到你的\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}That's why I'm afraid I can't help you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.93,0:57:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奥罗瑞小姐 我并不关心你是否知情的问题\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Well, I wouldn't worry overmuch about information, Miss o'Rory,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:46.01,0:57:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然人们都特别喜欢强调信息的重要性 但并非一直如此\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}because, you know, people always put "information" in quotes, but it isn't always like that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:49.44,0:57:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的意思是说 大家知道很多事 却并未意识到这一点\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I mean, people just don't realize how much they know.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.91,0:57:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比如 你就正好知道保险员的名字\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}For instance, you happen to know your agent's name.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.77,0:57:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这类信息我这上面都好好写着呢\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Mmm-hmm. I have all that information right here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:57.91,0:58:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其实我对别的信息更感兴趣\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I'm more interested in the other kind,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:00.81,0:58:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最后都可归结为一个词\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}which all really boils down to one word.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:06.26,0:58:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奥罗瑞小姐 你现在住在这么\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Do you live here now, Miss o'Rory?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:08.35,0:58:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我现在是住在这\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Oh, well, I'm here now, of course.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.43,0:58:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是临时这样 还是长期住在这\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Is that a temporary or a permanent arrangement?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:14.33,0:58:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得尼基需要母亲的关怀\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I think Nicky needs a mother.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:16.64,0:58:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然如此\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Of course.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.38,0:58:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我想问问你说的“一个词”是什么\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Um, what was that word? Excuse me?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:20.96,0:58:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你刚才说的 最后都可归结为一个词\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Well, you said it all boiled down to one word?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:24.74,0:58:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是么\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Did I?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:26.10,0:58:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦对\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Oh! Yes!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.19,0:58:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都可以归结为一个词 巧合\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Yes, it all boils down to one word, coincidence.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.14,0:58:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这种情况在歌剧里很常见  巧合嘛\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}That happens in the opera a lot. Coincidence.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.69,0:58:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}阿伊达：意大利歌剧家威尔第作的一部歌剧
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.69,0:58:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 阿伊达\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Yeah, sure. Aida.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.85,0:58:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}塞维利亚理发师：罗西尼所作歌剧
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.85,0:58:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,《塞维利亚理发师》 是的 很搞笑\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Uh, Barber of Seville. It's just... It gets ridiculous.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:38.87,0:58:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是现实生活中巧合是很少发生的\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}But in real life doesn't happen that much.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:42.12,0:58:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果巧合经常发生的话 那就不再是巧合了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}No. I guess if it did, it would stop being a coincidence.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.64,0:58:48.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是巧合和我们的保险合同无关 奥罗瑞小姐\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Yeah, see, it's not the policy, Miss o'Rory.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.15,0:58:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主要谈的是这个索赔的问题\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}It's the claim.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:49.45,0:58:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个索赔的案子中的巧合情况 就像一面面小红旗\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}See, a coincidence on a claim, that's like a... That's like a little red flag{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.84,0:58:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给我们提个醒 让我们加以注意\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}that makes us sit up and take notice.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.57,0:58:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这起案子中有不少这样的小红旗\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}And this claim has a bunch of little red flags on it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:58.30,0:59:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,具体是什么样的情况呢\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}What kind of red flag?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:01.66,0:59:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没什么好担心的\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Nothing to worry about.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.60,0:59:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相信我 我来只是为了拔除这些红旗 这是日常程序\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Believe me, I'm just here to chase down all those little red flags. It's very routine.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.60,0:59:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们只是需要澄清疑问\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}We just need to have them explained to us{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.20,0:59:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再支付索赔\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}before we can send out a check.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.68,0:59:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有疑问了我们会赔偿的 毫无疑问\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}The claim will be honored, of course.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.78,0:59:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 挺好的 - 当然 我们来看看啊\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Hmm, that's good. - Oh, sure. Let's just take a look here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:15.75,0:59:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我所注意到的第一面红旗\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}So the first little red flag that I noticed{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:21.00,0:59:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是三月三日\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}was that March 3rd,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:24.45,0:59:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出事前的三个月\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}about three months before the incident,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.04,0:59:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,投保金额大幅度增加了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}the amount of the whole part of the policy was substantially increased.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.14,0:59:33.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不太寻常\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}It's kind of unusual.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.89,0:59:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你应该不知道其中原因吧\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I don't suppose you know anything about that?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:38.25,0:59:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Mmm-hmm. I do.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:39.58,0:59:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是加德纳的主意\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}That was Gardner's idea.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.71,0:59:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 好的\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}It was, huh?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.61,0:59:47.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那好\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Okay.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.14,0:59:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有什么疑问呢 我来看看\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}What else have we got? We've got... Oh.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.33,0:59:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个合同中有多项索赔请求 这个倒是很常见了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}More than one claim on the policy. That's always a red flag.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:56.41,0:59:57.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是说萝丝出车祸的时候也索赔了么\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}The claim from Rose's car accident?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.92,1:00:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 他在这上面可是狠赚了一笔呢\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Yeah, he stung us good on that one.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.48,1:00:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这倒没什么问题 我们保险公司就是干这个的\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Well, that's okay. That's what we're here for.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:03.74,1:00:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,银行说他有三个月没有还房贷\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}The bank says he hasn't made his payments for his home loan in three months.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:07.25,1:00:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是这样的 情况不太好\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Oh. Well, times have been a little tight around here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.45,1:00:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加德纳做生意的时候损失了我们的全部积蓄\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Gardner lost our savings when he started his own business.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:14.84,1:00:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Is that right?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:18.15,1:00:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我来看看还有什么\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}What else have we got?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:21.38,1:00:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这还有一点疑问\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Here's another little red flag.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.78,1:00:25.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我此前都没有注意到这一点\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I didn't even notice this one before.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.87,1:00:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大约五个月前 洛奇先生\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Uh, about five months ago, Mr. Lodge{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.56,1:00:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,撤消了与我们签订的价值5000美元的人寿保险合同\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}redeemed $5,000 worth of his whole life policy with us.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.12,1:00:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们很容易觉察到这样的细节\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}We always like to notice things like that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:38.07,1:00:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尼基\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Nicky!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.39,1:00:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尼基 回你的房间去\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Nicky, get back in your room.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:48.39,1:00:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪来的 滚哪去\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Go back to where you came from!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:55.39,1:00:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,离开这里\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Get the hell out of here!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.69,1:01:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很抱歉 那钱是准备用来支付尼基未来的大学学费的\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I'm sorry. That money's for Nicky's college education.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.29,1:01:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是这钱你们买了信托基金之类的?\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I guess you put it in a trust fund or something?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:10.01,1:01:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想来杯咖啡么\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Would you like a cup of coffee?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:11.99,1:01:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那真是再好不过了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}That would be absolutely terrific.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:13.87,1:01:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Thank you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:17.51,1:01:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很抱歉因为这些事打扰您 但这些事是很重要的\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I'm sorry to be such a pest. I mean, this stuff isn't very important,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:21.57,1:01:25.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以跟你讲讲我以前遇到的几起骗保案例\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}but I tell you, I could put you on the floor with some of the scams I've seen.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:26.30,1:01:28.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想起那些事都会笑出声\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I've got to smile just thinking about them.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:28.71,1:01:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,几年前有一个人\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I mean, I had this one guy couple of years ago,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:30.99,1:01:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他自己的服装店烧毁了 要求赔偿\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}he put in a claim for his clothing store burned down.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.93,1:01:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你肯定会觉得这故事难以置信\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}You're not gonna believe this.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:34.40,1:01:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们在现场发现了几个汽油桶 上面写有“尤拉·梅”\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}We find a couple of gas cans in there with Eulah May printed on them.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.23,1:01:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是他妻子的名字\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}It's his wife's name.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:39.95,1:01:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是他从自己的游艇上搞来的\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}It's the name of his pleasure boat where he got the cans from.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:45.63,1:01:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我估计他是觉得这些铝制桶子应该会一起烧掉吧 不知道他是怎么想的\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I guess he thought those aluminum cans were gonna burn up or something. I don't know what he thought!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:49.52,1:01:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有那些汽车保险案 谢谢\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}And cars. Thank you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:51.42,1:01:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你肯定难以置信 人们是怎么对待自己的车的\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}You wouldn't believe what people do to their cars{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:53.17,1:01:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就因为出了点小毛病\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}just because something's a little wrong with the transmission.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:55.53,1:01:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们就觉得能敲保险公司的竹杠\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}They figure they can fleece us for the whole thing.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:58.06,1:02:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当报废车处理啊 然后报失啊\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Sell 'em for scrap, report 'em stolen.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:00.34,1:02:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些汽车修理厂的人我们都会打点好的\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}See, but the body shop guy knows we pay a bounty for those things.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:03.91,1:02:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就这周 这边半个街区的人都来找我们的麻烦\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Mmm. Yeah, I mean, just this week, half your block tried to tap us{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:06.49,1:02:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就因为你边上的这位新邻居\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}for homeowner's because of your new neighbors.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:08.71,1:02:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你敢信么 就因为来了位新邻居\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Can you believe it? How about them neighbors!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:14.98,1:02:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噢 抱歉\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Oh, excuse me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:22.33,1:02:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是你像我一样在这行干久了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}You've been in this business long as I have,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:25.06,1:02:26.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就会对这种事有敏锐的嗅觉\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}you develop a nose for hanky-panky.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.14,1:02:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每起案件仿佛就像有味道似的\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}'Cause it smells, you know?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:30.49,1:02:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那种淡淡的味道\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}It's got this faint aroma.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:33.43,1:02:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有些闻起来很不妙 有些就很正常 你懂我的意思么\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}This smells bad. That smells good. You know what I mean?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:38.87,1:02:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是这个嘛\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}But this one?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:40.90,1:02:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个案子嘛\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}This particular case here?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:44.55,1:02:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,闻起来没有那种淡淡的味道 - 谢天谢地\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Does not have that faint aroma. - Thank goodness for that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:47.90,1:02:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而是恶臭难闻\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Nah, this one stinks.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:49.91,1:02:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我从刚下高速路来这的路上就有这种感觉了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}This one... I've been smelling this one since I got off the turnpike.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:53.21,1:02:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的天 简直太臭了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Jesus, does it stink!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:55.42,1:02:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你跟加德纳睡过吧\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}You sleep with Gardner, do you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:57.70,1:02:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I beg your pardon!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:59.53,1:03:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道这跟我没什么关系\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Well, you know, that's none of my business,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:01.99,1:03:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我得跟你们说 这种事是遗臭万年的\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}but I've got to tell you, that kind of nonsense, it can come back and haunt you down the road.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:05.69,1:03:07.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是你们想办法把她弄死的话\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}If you killed her, I mean.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:08.94,1:03:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么敢\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}How dare you{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:10.39,1:03:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的姐姐尸骨未寒 你来我家里开这种玩笑\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}come into this home when my sister is dead{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:13.80,1:03:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还扯什么旗子和理发室的淡\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}and make jokes about flags and the barber of seville!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.43,1:03:19.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我保证 奥罗瑞女士 我来绝对不是开玩笑\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Oh, I assure you, Miss o'Rory, I am anything but joking.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:19.68,1:03:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得 根据我的经验 没有哪个蠢货\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}You see, in my experience, nobody's stupid enough{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:21.31,1:03:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会在杀妻之前提高投保金额的\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}to increase their insurance policy just before they kill their wife.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:24.43,1:03:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要告诉你一点 加德纳·洛奇肯定不是蠢货\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}If there's one thing you can be sure of, it's that Gardner Lodge isn't stupid.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.31,1:03:29.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我同意 库珀先生 那这么说来 你自己是完完全全的错了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Oh, I agree. So you've just proved yourself wrong, Mr. Cooper.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:29.69,1:03:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这些是我编的\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I made it up.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:31.49,1:03:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你编的? - 我编的\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}You made it up? I made it up.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.06,1:03:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他没有增加萝丝的投保金额 我只是钓鱼而已\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}He didn't take out more insurance on Rose. I was just fishing.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:36.26,1:03:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我调查每起案子都这样 我是去钓鱼的\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I do it on every claim. I go fishing.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.39,1:03:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你说 这次我可算抓住一处马脚了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}And you know what? This time I caught a whopper.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:40.61,1:03:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}What?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:41.79,1:03:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你用的是"我们"\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}You said "we."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:43.70,1:03:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}What?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:44.68,1:03:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说的是“加德纳失去了我们的全部积蓄”\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}"We lost our savings "when Gardner tried to start his own business."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:48.49,1:03:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说的是我们 而不是他们\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}"We lost our," not "they lost their."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:51.78,1:03:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赶紧走人 要不然我报警了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I think you should leave before I call the police.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:55.23,1:03:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你报警啊\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Call them.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:56.25,1:03:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你说 我们去街那头\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Hell, you know what? Let's just walk down the street.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:58.26,1:03:59.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那一头就有不少警察\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}There's a dozen of them standing a block away.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:59.53,1:04:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你滚出我的房子 - 你的房子\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}You get out of my house. Your house?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:02.30,1:04:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,滚出去 滚出去\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Oh! Get out! Get out. Get out, you!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:05.76,1:04:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我爱我的姐姐 我爱她的孩子\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I loved my sister, and I love her son!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:08.52,1:04:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也爱她的丈夫吧\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}You love her husband, too?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:12.65,1:04:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟洛奇先生说 我晚上会再来的\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}You tell Mr. Lodge I'll be back this evening.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:14.61,1:04:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们今晚可以聊聊\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}We can have a chat about it then.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:48.99,1:04:50.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你今晚请个假 - 你说什么\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}You're taking the night off. What?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:51.06,1:04:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你今晚请个假 我有更重要的事要派你去做\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}You're taking the night off. I've got more important things for you to do.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:53.68,1:04:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你疯了吧 兄弟\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}You're crazy, man.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:56.14,1:04:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斯坦霍普会来给你打掩护的 我们有正事干\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I got Stanhope to come in and cover for you. We've got business.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:59.31,1:05:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好好 什么事 说话别这么大声\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}All right. What is it? And don't talk so loud.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:02.80,1:05:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙很难缠\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}This guy's a fucking hard-on, is what it is.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:05.98,1:05:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他昨晚挂了我的电话\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}He hung up on me last night.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:09.04,1:05:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他不在乎我们了 我觉得他这是准备搞我们\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}He doesn't care. I think he's getting ready to fuck us.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:12.32,1:05:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他搞不了我们\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}He can't fuck us.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:14.13,1:05:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就对了嘛\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}That's right!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:24.19,1:05:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}门卫
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.01,1:05:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你说 这是那家伙最后一次耍我们了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I'm telling you, this is the last time that clown's gonna ignore us.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:31.98,1:05:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我要你今晚请假\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}That's why you're taking the night off.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:34.14,1:05:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把那女的和小孩都搞定喽\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Take care of the kid and the lady.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:37.41,1:05:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等他回来了 给他好好提个醒\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Give him something to think about when he gets home.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:39.67,1:05:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他妈的又搞两个人? 我觉得还是不要吧\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Two more fucking people? I don't know if I can get into that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:42.14,1:05:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你说 你没得选\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I'm telling you, you ain't got any choice.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:44.77,1:05:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要么我们出手 要么等着他搞我们\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}It's either that, or he fucks us!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:47.44,1:05:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙不理我们 不回复我们\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}The guy don't respond, he don't respond.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:49.05,1:05:50.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那可是两条人命啊 兄弟\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Two people, man!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:51.26,1:05:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听着 如果你连一个女的和一个孩子都搞不懂\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Look, if you can't take care of a kid and a lady,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:57.03,1:05:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道这意味着什么吗\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}you know what that means?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:00.09,1:06:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那估计你他妈的就是个废物了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}It means you're a fucking liability.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:37.91,1:07:40.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加德纳 我很抱歉 真的很抱歉\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Gardner, I'm sorry. I'm so, so sorry.{\r}
