Dialogue: 0,1:25:55.81,1:25:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尼基\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Nicky?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:30.94,1:26:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把枪给我\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Give me that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:22.01,1:27:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这些人禽兽不如\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}These people are animals.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:27.42,1:27:29.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们夺走了我们的一切\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}They took everything from us.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:32.53,1:27:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们杀了你\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}They took your{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:34.22,1:27:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玛格丽特阿姨\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}aunt maggie,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:37.25,1:27:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,米奇 杀了你的妈妈\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Mitch, your mom.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:46.06,1:27:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要你远离那个黑人男孩\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I want you to stay away from that colored boy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:50.43,1:27:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你听明白了么\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}You hear me?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:52.70,1:27:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你会报警么\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Are you gonna call the police?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:55.33,1:27:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们谈完了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I'll call the police{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:58.64,1:28:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会报警的\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}when we finish our talk.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:28:05.46,1:28:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Now,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:28:08.50,1:28:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这些禽兽不如的家伙夺走了我们的一切\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}these animals took everything from us.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:28:11.42,1:28:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们要保持...\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}And we need to make sense...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:28:18.81,1:28:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你 这都是你干的\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}It was you. You did all of this.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:28:43.71,1:28:45.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得自己知道什么\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}What do you think you know,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:28:45.82,1:28:47.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小伙子?\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}big man?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:28:57.29,1:28:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这些事我都很清楚\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Because I know a lot of things.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:28:59.63,1:29:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成年人就是这样\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}That's the case with being a grownup.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:03.66,1:29:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你必须做出决定\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}You have to make decisions.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:09.61,1:29:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,决定怎么样对我们这个家最好\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Decisions like what's best for the family.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:15.45,1:29:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁有用\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Who's being helpful.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:19.07,1:29:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁是累赘\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Who's a liability.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:23.28,1:29:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你应该知道累赘这个词的意思吧 尼基\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}You know what that word means, Nicky?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:31.87,1:29:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看这些人\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}You see, these men{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:35.06,1:29:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杀了你的妈妈\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}killed your mom.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:40.18,1:29:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后他们回来\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}And then they came back.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:42.98,1:29:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以说是 杀人灭口吧\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Tie up loose ends, so to speak.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:49.23,1:29:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他杀了你的阿姨玛格丽特\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}He killed your aunt maggie.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:53.22,1:29:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捅死了你的叔叔米奇\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Stabbed your uncle Mitch.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:00.84,1:30:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像他们还没杀够\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}As if that weren't bad enough,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:04.59,1:30:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他杀了你\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}then he killed you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:09.43,1:30:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在厨房里杀了你\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Right here in the kitchen.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:14.86,1:30:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后我开枪杀了他\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Then I shot him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:18.79,1:30:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他也捅了我几刀\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Oh, he cut me a few times.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:22.91,1:30:24.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许这儿\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Maybe here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:26.75,1:30:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这儿\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:28.94,1:30:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正是没什么生命危险的伤\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Nothing too life-threatening.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:33.90,1:30:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警官\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}"Officer,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:35.90,1:30:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我竭尽全力想要救下我的孩子\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I did everything I could to save my boy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:41.08,1:30:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但他深受重伤\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}"His injuries were just too great.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:45.03,1:30:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唉\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}"Well,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:46.60,1:30:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他现在和他妈妈在一起了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}"he's with his mama now.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:51.40,1:30:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他成了天堂里的小天使\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}"He's the littlest angel in heaven."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:30:58.81,1:31:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是你\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}That's you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:01.92,1:31:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小天使\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Little angel.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:11.05,1:31:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或者\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Or...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:15.03,1:31:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们一起打电话报警\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}...we call the police together.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:17.99,1:31:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告诉他们 这些人杀了我们的家人\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}We tell them how these men killed our family.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:20.61,1:31:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能活下来真是幸运\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}How we feel lucky to be alive.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:28.06,1:31:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尼基 你去过阿鲁巴岛么\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}You ever heard of Aruba, Nicky?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:32.54,1:31:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们会申请\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}We'll tell the papers{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:34.70,1:31:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要那些保险赔款\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}we don't want that insurance money,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:36.47,1:31:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我们要用这些钱重建我们的生活\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}but we're gonna use it to rebuild our lives.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:41.31,1:31:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们会去\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Our lives{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:44.09,1:31:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一个很远的地方生活\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}far away{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:46.01,1:31:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们会淡忘这里\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}from the memory of this place.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:52.31,1:31:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们坐上飞机 去阿鲁巴岛\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}And then we get on a plane and go to Aruba.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:58.38,1:32:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在岛上买个大房子\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}And we buy a big house on the beach.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:02.92,1:32:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重新开始\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}And we start over.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:18.05,1:32:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以 小伙子\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}So, big man,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:22.80,1:32:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的大小伙子\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}my big grown man,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:28.61,1:32:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要做出这样的重大决定了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}you've got a big decision to make.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:45.43,1:32:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好想想吧\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Take your time.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:49.85,1:32:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天是周日\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}It's sunday.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:56.70,1:32:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比肯镇的周日\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Sunday in Suburbicon.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:04.89,1:33:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们有的是时间\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}We've got all the time in the world.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:49.05,1:33:51.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 谢谢 - 没事的 女士\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Thank you. Of course, ma'am.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:51.45,1:33:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一位警察被打的头破血流\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}One policeman got his head busted open.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:53.44,1:33:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一辆救火车在拉法叶街发生车祸 一人身亡\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}And a fire truck hit and killed a man down on Lafayette street.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:57.33,1:33:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,另外三位还是四位伤员送往了医院\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}And three or four others ended up in the hospital.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:00.64,1:34:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有萝丝·洛奇 唉\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}And Rose Lodge! This...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:04.95,1:34:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迈尔斯一家搬到这之前从没出过这样的事\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}None of this ever happened before the Mayers moved here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:09.71,1:34:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是一个平静的小镇 你有没有听说过什么关于迈尔斯一家的谣言?\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}This is a peaceful town. Have you heard any rumors about the Mayers?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:13.49,1:34:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听过很多很多谣言\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Oh, dozens and dozens of rumors.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:16.11,1:34:19.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听说全国有色人种协进会给他们提供财力支持\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Oh, that he was being paid by the NAACP.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:19.48,1:34:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能背后有共党分子操纵他们 可能有犹太人插手\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}That the reds were behind it, that the jews were behind it,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:23.24,1:34:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,形形色色的组织给他们撑腰\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}that this group and that group were behind it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:27.05,1:34:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有各种各样的谣言\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}There were all kinds of rumors.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:28.25,1:34:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得有些谣言是故意传的 有些只是人们大惊小怪罢了\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I guess some of them were being spread deliberately. Some were just the result of hysteria.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:32.79,1:34:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是觉得应该压迫他们\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}I don't feel that they should be oppressed.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:35.83,1:34:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我搬到这里\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}But I moved here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:37.51,1:34:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一个主要原因\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}One of the main reasons{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:42.81,1:34:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是这是一个完全由白人组成的社区\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}was because it was a white community.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:44.43,1:34:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发生在杰拉尔德·麦克洛伊\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}And that......The story of Gerald Mccloy{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:46.18,1:34:49.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这位小男孩 身上的奇怪故事\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}and the strange thing that happened to that little boy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:51.32,1:34:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们说这一切都开始于杰拉尔德两岁的时候\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}They say it all started when Gerald was two.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:54.42,1:34:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,二岁的孩子差不多刚刚学会说话 至少他们中的大部分都是这样的\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}That's the age kids start talking. Least most of them do.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:01.11,1:35:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当他开始说话的时候 你知道他说了什么吗\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}Well, when he started talking, you know what he said?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:03.65,1:35:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他说出来的不是词语 而是\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}He didn't talk words. He went, "boing, boing,"{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:07.24,1:35:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哔哔\N{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14}instead.{\r}

